cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR. 

The paper is about action recognition, which is a subfield of computer vision. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely category. The paper also discusses machine learning algorithms and evaluation protocols, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.MM (Multimedia), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the dataset is crawled from the Internet, which could also make it relevant to cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
